headline.print_headline: Hendrick Ranks California as 1 of Toughest Defeats
headline.main: Hendrick Ranks California as 1 of Toughest Defeats

lead_paragraph: It was a long cross-country flight home for Rick Hendrick after the team owner watched victory slip away for two of his drivers at Auto Club Speedway.
